Credit facilities

As of September 30, 2023, and 2022, Siemens has €7.45 billion lines of credit, which are unused. The €7.0 billion syndicated loan facility matures in February 2026. In September 2023, the unused €450 million revolving bilateral credit facility was extended to September 2024. The facilities are for general corporate purposes.

